quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  5,104,"Si …ďee fefindotoo…ďe fenaande e hoore Alla wi'anaama : "Aree e ko Alla Jippini kon ka Qur'aanaare, e suuna Nulaa…óo Makko on (yo o his), fii no anndiron haram e halal, …ďe wi'ay : "Yonii men kon ko men tawri maw…ďe amen …ďen immorde e pi…ďe e golle", honno …óum yonirta …ďe nde tawnoo maw…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen anndaano hay e huunde, …ďe feewataano kadi e goonga kan?! Ko …ďur…óo …ďe majjere tun jokkata …ďee majju…ďe."
  5,105,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe ! Hino fawii on pittaali mon …óin : wa…ó…óitoree…ói gollugol ko mo∆ī∆īani …ói. Majjere yim…ďe …ďen lorrataa on si onn feewii onon ; feewiron yamirgol mo∆ī∆īere ha…óa Ňčo√Īere. Ko faade ka Alla tun woni ruttorde mon nden √Ďalnde Darngal on denndaangal ; O Habra on kon ko gollayno…óon aduna, O Yo…ďita on …óum."
  5,106,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe ! Si maayde nden …ďa…ótike go…ó…óo e mon, maande mayre he…ďii mo, yo o seedintin wasiyee makko on nun…óu…ďe …ói…óo juul…ďe maa wor…ďe …ói…óo heere…ďe -si on he…ďaali juul…ďe, si on setike maayde nden yanii e mon ton. Si on sikkitike seedeeyaagal ma…ď…ďe ngal, darnee …ďe baawo julde woo, …ďe woondira Alla : …ďe yeeyirtaa ge…ďal ma…ď…ďe ngal coggu, hay si tawii ko si…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe, e wonnde suu…óataa seedee Alla, e wonnde si …ďe wa…óii …óum, haray …ďe jeyaama e bakkondim…ďe …ďen."
  5,107,"Si fee√Īii …ďaawoo woondoore nden wonnde …ďe fenu, haray yo …ói…óo woondu maa seeditoo ∆īetta darnde ma…ď…ďe nden, jeyaa…ďe e yim…ďe maay…óo on, …ďe wonndira Alla wonnde : "Pellet, ko seedee amen on e fenannde ma…ď…ďe nden …ďuri jojjude e dii seedee ma…ď…ďe on ; men seeditaaki fenaande, menen si men wa…óii …óum, haray ko men jeyaa…ďe e too√Īu…ďe yawti keeri Alla …óin"."
  5,108,"Ko jantaa ko'o e wonndoore seedee…ďe …ďen …ói…óo …ďaawo julde nden, tuma nde woondoore ma…ď…ďe nden sikkitaa, e ruttugol seedee ma…ď…ďe on, ko …óum …ďuri …ďa…ótaade nde …ďe addata seedee e hoore nden …óon ; wata …ďe waylu woondoore nden maa …ďe janfoo e mayre, ko …óum kadi …ďuri …ďa…ótaade nde …ďe hulata yo woondoore ndonndi nden ruttetee …ďaawo woondoore ma…ď…ďe nden, …ďe seeditoo ko lunndii seedee ma…ď…ďe on …ďe wirtoo. Hulee Alla accon fenannde e janfa ka woondooje e ka seedagol, nanon ja…ďon ko waaja…óon. Alla fewnataa …ďen yaltu…ďe e …óoftaare."